    "long_instructions": "\r\n## What is Coding with Music? \r\n\r\n\r\n#### Coding with Music is a short, accessible curriculum for grades 3-5 that teaches programming through music creation. Students learn to code melodies, loops, and interactive compositions in a fun, engaging way while meeting accessibility standards.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n"
